ces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1687975eb07de1ce54ded807431ecd8688090839","tid":420893,"uid":86791,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:28:09.000Z","msg":"個陣aim 1 點知拎到個3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cb0191371f29368e6f0ff2136c3a9b8971e3f1","tid":420893,"uid":51715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"用得多咪有3<br />\n埋大hd用英文讀其實已經對你學英文有一定作用<br />\n你無興趣好難浸  可以試下loop paper3錄音既<br />\n買本reading 慢慢做下有得<br />\n<br />\n利伸 -6 retake 2升3"},{"pid":"22f10514cb250d5ae5de7059db3ea877642405d0","tid":420893,"uid":72566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"睇readings,完"},{"pid":"7ad89b7a8e7592f76b2c73fda793b22808e06458","tid":420893,"uid":51715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:23:53.000Z","msg":"同埋我覺得金娜娜個堆英文note幾淺白<br />\n不妨down黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423c166a23ee0cf7a03cc48889628ed30c9e16dc","tid":420893,"uid":75773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:04:22.000Z","msg":"2升3<br />\n金娜娜 notes + 私補清 concepts + 定期作文操卷"},{"pid":"02185e9a2aa4aa3c9016c605918a48c24854f30b","tid":420893,"uid":135817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"作文背定format 或一大段有用既句子 <br />\n唔好錯咁多grammar<br />\nSpeaking扮下野都會有4<br />\n拉埋就有3<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc5d94ab0f1c0952834b5ff788f07f90dd0d70f","tid":420893,"uid":139605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"認真睇英文youtube係有用嘅<br />\n唔一定要睇咩教英文個D片(因為真係好_悶，完全係消磨緊自己對英文嘅熱情)<br />\n睇youtubers嘅打機片，生活片，雜談片，英劇美劇乜都得，最緊要係全英，同埋你有興趣<br />\n字幕就盡量唔好開喇，真係唔明就開英文或者自動翻譯個個啦<br />\n<br />\n另外練好D grammar tense個D基本野，再練下D簡單嘅句式(難嘅學黎都晒時間，到時夾硬用用錯左仲樣衰)。到時簡簡單單作篇小學雞文，唔好比個marker捉到你有錯就得。"},{"pid":"913728150d0a0d13e0b2a450c14c1